CONTRIBUTOR LICENSE AGREEMENT
=============================

By submitting contributions to this project, you agree to the
Developer Certificate of Origin (DCO). Sign off your commits with:

    git commit -s -m "Your commit message"

This certifies that you have the right to submit the contribution
and agree to license it under the same terms as the project.
